arStrings.szText: "Will the heart be enough to free Neyrelle?"
Go, and find out. I’ll hang back for Eru. When he’s back on his feet, I’ll send him to meet you. The council will want to know what’s happened.
And, listen...you did what was needed, in there. My circle will not soon forget.
